########error Selenium Java 4.1.3 java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: org/openqa/selenium/WebDriver

You at least need to add these external JARS:

selenium-api-4.1.3
selenium-remote-driver-4.1.3
selenium-chromium-driver-4.1.3
selenium-chrome-driver-4.1.3
(all in the folder 'lib')


###eror SLF4J:Failed to load class "org.slf4j.impl.StaticLoggerBinder


To solve this error, I checked if I had slf4j-api-1.7.36.jar file and I added slf4j-simple-1.7.36.jar. 
I downloaded it from https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/slf4j/slf4j-simple/1.7.36/slf4j-simple-1.7.36.jar